{"entity":{"id":"rec1zm3eWl3OT8FEI","type":"chapter","slug":"rec1zm3eWl3OT8FEI","label":"Ps.84","rawId":"rec1zm3eWl3OT8FEI","book":{"id":"recKXZXO6cJwk2SxO","type":"book","slug":"ps","label":"Psalms","subtitle":"Poetry-Wisdom","count":2461,"description":"150 chapters, 1026 people, 118 places"}},"stats":{"verses":12,"people":2,"places":2,"events":0},"nodes":[{"id":"rec1zm3eWl3OT8FEI","type":"chapter","group":"focus","label":"Ps.84","slug":"ps_84","score":12},{"id":"recKXZXO6cJwk2SxO","type":"book","group":"book","label":"Psalms","slug":"ps","score":2461},{"id":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"God","slug":"god_1324","score":9},{"id":"recsU2ZSdzBvDqzgI","type":"person","group":"mentioned","label":"Jacob (Israel)","slug":"israel_682","score":1},{"id":"recI0bhf2ewWIHMRC","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Valley of Baca","slug":"valley_of_baca_1199","score":1},{"id":"reczPjeq0UdahiRrn","type":"place","group":"mentioned","label":"Zion","slug":"zion_1263","score":1}],"links":[{"source":"rec1zm3eWl3OT8FEI","target":"recKXZXO6cJwk2SxO","label":"part of"},{"source":"rec1zm3eWl3OT8FEI","target":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec1zm3eWl3OT8FEI","target":"recsU2ZSdzBvDqzgI","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec1zm3eWl3OT8FEI","target":"recI0bhf2ewWIHMRC","label":"mentions"},{"source":"rec1zm3eWl3OT8FEI","target":"reczPjeq0UdahiRrn","label":"mentions"}],"verses":[{"id":"recZ34hxdZPncgEoQ","ref":"Ps.84.1","text":"How amiable are thy tabernacles, O LORD of hosts!"},{"id":"recXoKUUO6yANrMgp","ref":"Ps.84.2","text":"My soul longeth, yea, even fainteth for the courts of the LORD: my heart and my flesh crieth out for the living God."},{"id":"rec8WRkoNFj4xMFxl","ref":"Ps.84.3","text":"Yea, the sparrow hath found an house, and the swallow a nest for herself, where she may lay her young, even thine altars, O LORD of hosts, my King, and my God."},{"id":"recmjQvvSKDUtv89u","ref":"Ps.84.4","text":"Blessed are they that dwell in thy house: they will be still praising thee. Selah."},{"id":"recVIFHM0Yi92m8ib","ref":"Ps.84.5","text":"Blessed is the man whose strength is in thee; in whose heart are the ways of them."},{"id":"recu90mLUqaT1Ob0K","ref":"Ps.84.6","text":"Who passing through the valley of Baca make it a well; the rain also filleth the pools."},{"id":"recXjcklxp69jr6E7","ref":"Ps.84.7","text":"They go from strength to strength, every one of them in Zion appeareth before God."},{"id":"reci4oqji4t4qABAu","ref":"Ps.84.8","text":"O LORD God of hosts, hear my prayer: give ear, O God of Jacob. Selah."}]}
